item.title: CVE-2022-3919|2024-08-03T01:20:58.778Z -- unknown -- jetpack%20crm
item.description: The Jetpack CRM WordPress plugin before 5.4.3 does not sanitise and escape its settings, allowing high privilege users such as admin to perform cross-Site Scripting attacks even when the unfiltered_html capability is disallowed.
